=== Addition or Subtraction Method

#eg[
  #linebreak()

  $
  3 x + 2 y = 12 quad quad ("Equation" 1) \
  
  2 x - 2 y = 4 quad quad ("Equation" 2) \
  $

  #linebreak()

  1. Add the equations

  $
  (3 x + 2 y) + (2 x - 2 y) = 12 + 4 \
  5 x = 16 \
  x = 16 / 5 \
  x = 3.2
  $

  2. Substitute 

  $
  3 (3.2) + 2 y = 12 \ 
  9.6 + 2 y = 12 \
  2y = 12 - 9.6
  y = 2.4 / 2 \
  y = 1.2
  $
